# ASINs — product pages (10-character ASINs starting with B0)
# Matches exactly /B0XXXXXXXXX
/B0[A-Z0-9]{8}  https://www.amazon.com/dp/:splat/?tag=dailydealsa0f-20  302

# Promo codes — single-segment paths that are NOT ASINs
# Matches /ANYTHING-ELSE that is one segment long
/:promo  https://www.amazon.com/promocode/:promo?tag=dailydealsa0f-20  302

